# plot price change

       aes(x = price_kg_rel_year_mon*100, y = species, col = factor(month))) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_vline(xintercept = 100, col = "red", alpha= 0.7) +
  xlim(0,200) + 
  scale_color_viridis(discrete=TRUE) +
